        "action": "Maintain the B1 English Language requirement for ILR",
        "additional_details": "We believe it\u2019s unfair for non-native English speakers to be required to have a higher academic level of English over UK-born citizens.",
        "background": "Scrap the planned B2 English language requirement and maintain the B1 requirement for qualifying for ILR, to bring it in line with a majority of UK citizens who have GCSE level English and may not have formal A-Level qualifications.",
